lead_paragraph: James Taylor put aside his disappointing Test form to produce a run-a-ball century as England crushed South Africa A by 163 runs in a warm-up game at the Diamond Oval on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Taylor Ton Spearheads Massive England Warm-Up Win
